  keywords = {Computer Science - Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition,Computer Science - Machine Learning},
  annotation = {TLDR: The AnchoreD multimodAl Physiological Transformer (ADAPT), a multimodal, scalable framework with two key components: aligning all modalities in the space of the strongest, richest modality (called anchor) to learn a joint embedding space, and a Masked Multimodal Transformer, leveraging both inter- and intra-modality correlations while handling missing modalities.},
